Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.12,0:00:22.20,OP中文,,0,0,0,,我们在零重力之中起舞
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.42,0:00:27.50,OP中文,,0,0,0,,飞速旅行到遥远的星际
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.44,0:00:35.44,OP中文,,0,0,0,,需要特殊的快递吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.92,0:00:38.00,OP中文,,0,0,0,,只需叫上Malo Korrigan
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.08,0:00:41.24,OP中文,,0,0,0,,但不是免费的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.62,0:00:48.37,OP中文,,0,0,0,,Malo Korrigan
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.92,0:00:52.02,OP中文,,0,0,0,,没人能打倒你
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.20,0:00:54.70,OP中文,,0,0,0,,Malo Korrigan
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.40,0:00:57.88,OP中文,,0,0,0,,生活在宇宙中
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.12,0:00:22.20,OP英文,,0,0,0,,We can dance in zero G
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.42,0:00:27.50,OP英文,,0,0,0,,Traveling fast far from galaxy
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.44,0:00:35.44,OP英文,,0,0,0,,Need a special delivery
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.92,0:00:38.00,OP英文,,0,0,0,,Just call Malo Korrigan
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.08,0:00:41.24,OP英文,,0,0,0,,But it's not free
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.62,0:00:48.37,OP英文,,0,0,0,,Malo Korrigan
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.92,0:00:52.02,OP英文,,0,0,0,,Nobody will bring you down
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.20,0:00:54.70,OP英文,,0,0,0,,Malo Korrigan
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.40,0:00:57.88,OP英文,,0,0,0,,live in space
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.02,0:01:08.30,MK副标,,0,0,0,,{\pos(480,462)}{\fad(780,780)}{\blur4}翻译、时间轴、后期：Bolshevik0
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.02,0:01:08.30,MK标题,,0,0,0,,{\pos(405,285)}{\fad(780,780)}{\blur4}#2              老兵
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.60,0:01:47.00,MK注释,,0,0,0,,注:\h飞船上的零部件按里程说使用寿命应该也行
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.80,0:01:23.17,MK英文,,0,0,0,,Jonas, don't let those thrusters give out.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.22,0:01:33.97,MK英文,,0,0,0,,Speck of dust blowing in a windstorm.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.75,0:01:36.35,MK英文,,0,0,0,,Judge one way of putting it.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.57,0:01:39.72,MK英文,,0,0,0,,They feel more like an ice cream cone
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.75,0:01:42.02,MK英文,,0,0,0,,stuck in the middle of {\u1}a go{\u0} volcano.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.60,0:01:45.02,MK英文,,0,0,0,,This black tritanium fuel cell was supposed to
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.02,0:01:47.00,MK英文,,0,0,0,,last another three trillion light-years.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.02,0:01:48.95,MK英文,,0,0,0,,Isn't it covered by a warranty?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.32,0:01:51.82,MK英文,,0,0,0,,Kid, you gotta be kidding.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.77,0:01:54.75,MK英文,,0,0,0,,I bought it from your godless brothers
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.77,0:01:56.50,MK英文,,0,0,0,,and I'll give them a piece on my mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.75,0:01:59.50,MK英文,,0,0,0,,Hang on old-timer cuz we're in for a rough landing.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.97,0:02:27.97,MK英文,,0,0,0,,Jonas, fire retrorockets 1, 2 and 3 at full power.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.25,0:03:10.82,MK英文,,0,0,0,,You were great baby.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.67,0:03:16.05,MK英文,,0,0,0,,Sorry it was so hard but you really came through.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.32,0:03:40.52,MK英文,,0,0,0,,Shouldn't you be wearing a spacesuit, princess?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.67,0:03:43.30,MK英文,,0,0,0,,The atmosphere on this planet isn't very comfortable.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.60,0:03:44.50,MK英文,,0,0,0,,Not for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.67,0:03:48.40,MK英文,,0,0,0,,But I like breathing carbon monoxide at sub-zero temperatures.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.70,0:03:49.80,MK英文,,0,0,0,,So what's the problem?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.65,0:03:52.30,MK英文,,0,0,0,,Well I'll tell you what the problem is?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.37,0:03:56.17,MK英文,,0,0,0,,Trying to find a tritanium fuel cell in this planetary junkyard.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.35,0:03:57.77,MK英文,,0,0,0,,It's not a junkyard.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.77,0:03:59.25,MK英文,,0,0,0,,It's more like a museum.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.50,0:04:03.30,MK英文,,0,0,0,,Every single vessel and weapon that was used in the Sewalik Wars
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.30,0:04:05.65,MK英文,,0,0,0,,is now gather and rust on this planet.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.95,0:04:19.52,MK英文,,0,0,0,,Galloping galaxies.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.52,0:04:21.85,MK英文,,0,0,0,,The thermal shield was damaged when we landed.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.47,0:04:24.60,MK英文,,0,0,0,,And I want to do extra repairs.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.35,0:04:34.20,MK英文,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I wanna be your lover.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.20,0:04:38.97,MK英文,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Maybe you'd do but I wanna be mad about you.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.50,0:04:42.32,MK英文,,0,0,0,,{\i1}You're still crying baby.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.57,0:04:43.65,MK英文,,0,0,0,,Want us to wait for you?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.72,0:04:44.47,MK英文,,0,0,0,,No thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.67,0:04:46.62,MK英文,,0,0,0,,Go look for a tritanium fuel cell.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.77,0:04:48.07,MK英文,,0,0,0,,Mark 87, man,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.10,0:04:50.87,MK英文,,0,0,0,,when I'm finished here I'll go prospective around.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.00,0:04:53.27,MK英文,,0,0,0,,Ten to one we will find it before you do.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.67,0:04:54.35,MK英文,,0,0,0,,Oh yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.57,0:04:57.57,MK英文,,0,0,0,,Cyana, you got a bet.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.52,0:05:00.47,MK英文,,0,0,0,,Say you two.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.50,0:05:03.45,MK英文,,0,0,0,,Maybe you should take all best you want. Just in case.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.57,0:05:05.60,MK英文,,0,0,0,,Not a chance.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.60,0:05:07.27,MK英文,,0,0,0,,Your proton gun is more dangerous
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.30,0:05:09.07,MK英文,,0,0,0,,than an overheated nuclear reactor.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.50,0:05:15.52,MK英文,,0,0,0,,So long.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.20,0:06:00.77,MK英文,,0,0,0,,Look at all the starfighters,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.82,0:06:02.82,MK英文,,0,0,0,,neutron missiles and bomber drones.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.95,0:06:04.20,MK英文,,0,0,0,,This place is crazy.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.32,0:06:05.87,MK英文,,0,0,0,,Wars are always crazy.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.92,0:06:08.25,MK英文,,0,0,0,,And the Sewalik Wars were crazier than the most.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.45,0:06:12.17,MK英文,,0,0,0,,On the other hand, the 12 mother planets grew so weary of fighting
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.47,0:06:15.40,MK英文,,0,0,0,,but they decided to unite
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.62,0:06:18.75,MK英文,,0,0,0,,and that's how the Cosmocratic League was born.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.00,0:06:20.00,MK英文,,0,0,0,,Let me try.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.77,0:06:27.32,MK英文,,0,0,0,,I love being humiliated.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.42,0:06:29.02,MK英文,,0,0,0,,Looks like I've won the bet.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.35,0:06:32.25,MK英文,,0,0,0,,Hey, Jonas. Is the mark 75 compatible?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.44,0:06:33.62,MK英文,,0,0,0,,You may think I'm saying this
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.67,0:06:35.07,MK英文,,0,0,0,,because of the bet but no.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.07,0:06:36.70,MK英文,,0,0,0,,We need at least two mark 87.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.97,0:06:37.62,MK英文,,0,0,0,,You sure?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.87,0:06:39.57,MK英文,,0,0,0,,At the academy I learned that it's all go...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.57,0:06:41.20,MK英文,,0,0,0,,Forget what you learn to the academy.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.27,0:06:44.05,MK英文,,0,0,0,,Those starchy old professors never set foot in an engine room.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.45,0:06:45.45,MK英文,,0,0,0,,Besides, I've got...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.50,0:06:50.25,MK英文,,0,0,0,,Jonas?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.42,0:06:53.25,MK英文,,0,0,0,,Jonas, come in.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.65,0:06:54.22,MK英文,,0,0,0,,Jonas!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.60,0:06:55.52,MK英文,,0,0,0,,He's not responding.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.62,0:06:56.32,MK英文,,0,0,0,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.62,0:06:58.25,MK英文,,0,0,0,,Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.47,0:07:11.92,MK英文,,0,0,0,,Cyana! Be careful!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.25,0:07:14.07,MK英文,,0,0,0,,You don't know what you're gonna find down there.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.95,0:07:23.05,MK英文,,0,0,0,,Jonas?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.05,0:07:39.25,MK英文,,0,0,0,,Jonas where are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.32,0:07:50.52,MK英文,,0,0,0,,Jonas!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.05,0:07:57.40,MK英文,,0,0,0,,Well, what did you find?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.72,0:08:00.65,MK英文,,0,0,0,,Our entire cargo of holographic screens has vanished
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.10,0:08:02.65,MK英文,,0,0,0,,and so has Jonas.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.05,0:08:12.02,MK英文,,0,0,0,,Malo, there may be a way to locate Jonas.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.05,0:08:13.60,MK英文,,0,0,0,,I'm listening.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.00,0:08:15.90,MK英文,,0,0,0,,If his communicator still functioning,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.97,0:08:18.17,MK英文,,0,0,0,,we should be able to home in on his frequency.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.47,0:08:23.35,MK英文,,0,0,0,,All right it's working.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.72,0:08:25.22,MK英文,,0,0,0,,His signal is straight ahead of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.52,0:08:27.20,MK英文,,0,0,0,,Range 5,000 meters.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.82,0:08:28.52,MK英文,,0,0,0,,and it's moving.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.40,0:08:34.77,MK英文,,0,0,0,,Hang in there old tracer.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.60,0:08:36.62,MK英文,,0,0,0,,We're on our way.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.67,0:08:54.77,MK英文,,0,0,0,,Range 2,000 meters. We're getting closer.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.67,0:09:15.67,MK英文,,0,0,0,,Signals very close now.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.12,0:09:17.75,MK英文,,0,0,0,,So why haven't we found him?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.42,0:09:19.75,MK英文,,0,0,0,,Jonas!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.10,0:09:22.72,MK英文,,0,0,0,,This is a joke cuz it isn't funny.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.05,0:09:23.82,MK英文,,0,0,0,,Oh no!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.32,0:09:31.95,MK英文,,0,0,0,,The signal isn't coming from here.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.17,0:09:32.97,MK英文,,0,0,0,,He may be alright.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.05,0:09:33.97,MK英文,,0,0,0,,Without his helmet?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.32,0:09:37.22,MK英文,,0,0,0,,I can survive in a frigid carbon monoxide atmosphere
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.27,0:09:38.35,MK英文,,0,0,0,,but Jonas can't.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.32,0:09:50.02,MK英文,,0,0,0,,Jonas.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.15,0:10:11.87,MK英文,,0,0,0,,Cyana, the signal's moving again.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.17,0:10:13.82,MK英文,,0,0,0,,The old codger's still alive
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.97,0:10:15.47,MK英文,,0,0,0,,and he's somewhere over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.45,0:10:42.37,MK英文,,0,0,0,,Get out of there.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.65,0:11:02.25,MK英文,,0,0,0,,Watch out.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.55,0:11:13.45,MK英文,,0,0,0,,Ah!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.07,0:12:03.12,MK英文,,0,0,0,,Cyana!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.35,0:12:07.57,MK英文,,0,0,0,,Where are we?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.35,0:12:11.67,MK英文,,0,0,0,,Inside an XP class transport rig,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.87,0:12:14.57,MK英文,,0,0,0,,one of the biggest vessels used during the Sewalik Wars.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.30,0:12:19.37,MK英文,,0,0,0,,I'm still getting a signal.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.80,0:12:21.27,MK英文,,0,0,0,,Jonas seems to be nearby.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.70,0:12:22.70,MK英文,,0,0,0,,Let's go check it out.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.45,0:12:26.20,MK英文,,0,0,0,,The thing that attacked us, do you have any idea what it is?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.87,0:12:29.45,MK英文,,0,0,0,,Probably a battle robot left over from the wars.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.80,0:12:31.75,MK英文,,0,0,0,,But I thought all the weapons were deactivated
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.75,0:12:32.90,MK英文,,0,0,0,,before being dumped here.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.22,0:12:35.80,MK英文,,0,0,0,,Seems like someone decided to break the rules.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.67,0:12:39.90,MK英文,,0,0,0,,If that's true then we have to notify the authorities about this.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.02,0:12:41.25,MK英文,,0,0,0,,Malo, look!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.57,0:12:44.65,MK英文,,0,0,0,,There's our missing cargo, the holographic screens.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.40,0:12:51.22,MK英文,,0,0,0,,But how did they end up in here?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.55,0:12:52.32,MK英文,,0,0,0,,I got a clue.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.82,0:12:59.65,MK英文,,0,0,0,,Stay still.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.00,0:13:13.62,MK英文,,0,0,0,,Go!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.57,0:13:25.50,MK英文,,0,0,0,,Combat unit FAR422 mission.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.50,0:13:29.57,MK英文,,0,0,0,,Defend frontlines and repel enemy attack against oppositions.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.57,0:13:34.70,MK英文,,0,0,0,,BA2568A125 sustained enemy attack.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.75,0:13:36.35,MK英文,,0,0,0,,Intruders neutralized.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.35,0:13:38.35,MK英文,,0,0,0,,Attempting to contact headquarters
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.40,0:13:41.17,MK英文,,0,0,0,,and submit urgent request for reinforcements.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.60,0:13:42.22,MK英文,,0,0,0,,Amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.45,0:13:44.72,MK英文,,0,0,0,,He thinks he's still fighting in the Sewalik Wars.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.97,0:13:47.87,MK英文,,0,0,0,,I guess some fool of a general didn't disconnect him properly.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.45,0:14:01.77,MK英文,,0,0,0,,Jonas is still close by.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.42,0:14:26.07,MK英文,,0,0,0,,Follow me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.62,0:14:40.52,MK英文,,0,0,0,,What are they?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.72,0:14:41.65,MK英文,,0,0,0,,Shh! Quiet.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.20,0:14:47.87,MK英文,,0,0,0,,More battle robots, a whole squadron of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.57,0:14:58.17,MK英文,,0,0,0,,Combat unit FAR422 attempt to contact headquarters has failed.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.07,0:15:06.27,MK英文,,0,0,0,,Combat unit FAR422 mission's defend frontlines
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.97,0:15:09.12,MK英文,,0,0,0,,Executing the technical operations
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.12,0:15:11.72,MK英文,,0,0,0,,to obtain a necessary reinforcements.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.72,0:15:36.16,MK英文,,0,0,0,,That metal monstrosity is reactivating
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.16,0:15:38.22,MK英文,,0,0,0,,the other robots using our cargo.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.62,0:15:39.87,MK英文,,0,0,0,,There is reinforcements.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.22,0:15:42.12,MK英文,,0,0,0,,He's building himself an army.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.00,0:15:47.30,MK英文,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.60,0:15:48.10,MK英文,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.22,0:15:50.35,MK英文,,0,0,0,,He has the same move with Jonas.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.72,0:15:55.57,MK英文,,0,0,0,,Jonas's signal is right under us.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.62,0:15:57.65,MK英文,,0,0,0,,But that's where the robot is.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.75,0:15:59.45,MK英文,,0,0,0,,Jonas is in the robot.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.95,0:16:01.05,MK英文,,0,0,0,,What are we gonna do?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.55,0:16:02.47,MK英文,,0,0,0,,We're gonna get him out.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.27,0:16:03.60,MK英文,,0,0,0,,Come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.95,0:16:27.45,MK英文,,0,0,0,,Combat unit FAR422 under attack by enemy forces.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.70,0:16:32.25,MK英文,,0,0,0,,Mission defend oppositions and eliminate intruders immediately.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.72,0:17:03.22,MK英文,,0,0,0,,You sure this is a good idea?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.25,0:17:04.95,MK英文,,0,0,0,,No, it's the only one I got.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.00,0:17:08.95,MK英文,,0,0,0,,Eliminating intruders! Eliminating intruders!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.57,0:17:49.02,MK英文,,0,0,0,,Eliminating intruders! Eliminating intruders! Eliminating intruders!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.02,0:17:53.52,MK英文,,0,0,0,,Follow me!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.40,0:18:22.97,MK英文,,0,0,0,,Jonas, can you hear me?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.87,0:18:32.15,MK英文,,0,0,0,,Combat unit FAR422......
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.92,0:18:40.55,MK英文,,0,0,0,,Jonas!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.90,0:18:51.17,MK英文,,0,0,0,,This is bad now.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.72,0:18:53.70,MK英文,,0,0,0,,The robot is downloading Jonas's mind
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.70,0:18:55.97,MK英文,,0,0,0,,into it's own operating systems.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.85,0:19:01.02,MK英文,,0,0,0,,Hang in there, old buddy.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.15,0:19:03.20,MK英文,,0,0,0,,%$^%@#
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.12,0:19:13.25,MK英文,,0,0,0,,Well, well.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.22,0:19:15.70,MK英文,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.45,0:19:18.97,MK英文,,0,0,0,,The central processor was made by the Consortium.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.32,0:19:22.50,MK英文,,0,0,0,,But the Consortium didn't exist during the Sewalik Wars.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.75,0:19:25.10,MK英文,,0,0,0,,I suspect that our friend Yago rigged this robot
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.10,0:19:27.20,MK英文,,0,0,0,,to build a secret army for the Consortium.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.85,0:19:28.95,MK英文,,0,0,0,,But he failed.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.05,0:19:38.52,MK英文,,0,0,0,,Eliminating intruders! Eliminating intruders! Eliminating intruders!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.87,0:20:35.35,MK英文,,0,0,0,,Jonas!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.12,0:20:38.70,MK英文,,0,0,0,,Jonas!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.15,0:20:42.12,MK英文,,0,0,0,,Speak to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.05,0:20:51.87,MK英文,,0,0,0,,Looks like I win that bet after all, you two.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.60,0:20:53.00,MK英文,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.17,0:20:55.27,MK英文,,0,0,0,,Look up there.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.07,0:20:57.67,MK英文,,0,0,0,,tritanium fuel cell.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.75,0:20:58.80,MK英文,,0,0,0,,It's a mark 87.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.95,0:20:59.95,MK英文,,0,0,0,,Yeah I found it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.60,0:21:03.82,MK英文,,0,0,0,,Jonas you're a crafty old {\u1}kittens{\u0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.82,0:21:06.30,MK英文,,0,0,0,,There's a dozens of mark 87s in here,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.00,0:21:09.85,MK英文,,0,0,0,,which will be able to sell to your godless brothers.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.55,0:21:13.30,MK英文,,0,0,0,,We're gonna end up making a tidy profit on this run.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.45,0:21:19.72,MK英文,,0,0,0,,But first I want to do some repair work on our robot.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.77,0:21:20.52,MK英文,,0,0,0,,Are you kidding?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.97,0:21:24.47,MK英文,,0,0,0,,The FAR422 has been deactivated for good.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.85,0:21:26.07,MK英文,,0,0,0,,That's what you think.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.17,0:21:29.07,MK英文,,0,0,0,,But I'm an even {\u1}crafty-year-old{\u0} cooler than you realize.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.00,0:21:33.57,MK英文,,0,0,0,,Since the robot had the good taste to trying download my knowledge,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.85,0:21:36.00,MK英文,,0,0,0,,I figured I'd teach him a few tricks.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.07,0:21:39.62,MK英文,,0,0,0,,Wipe out any trace of the Sewalik Wars or the Consortium.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.32,0:21:52.92,MK英文,,0,0,0,,{\u1}quiberon quasars {\u0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.92,0:21:54.20,MK英文,,0,0,0,,Does I ever go down?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.20,0:21:54.72,MK英文,,0,0,0,,Good.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.20,0:22:00.67,MK英文,,0,0,0,,What I was stuck on the inside of that oversized tin soldier,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.37,0:22:04.62,MK英文,,0,0,0,,I was convinced that I never eat... {\u1}come{\u0} again.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.47,0:22:09.47,MK英文,,0,0,0,,By the way, Jonas, exactly what kind of tricks did you teach that robot?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.55,0:22:13.50,MK英文,,0,0,0,,No! Nothing very complicated. Just a few basic peaceful procedures.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.60,0:22:16.62,MK英文,,0,0,0,,But I did give the robot my greatest talent.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.07,0:22:18.30,MK英文,,0,0,0,,Don't laugh, Kiwk Kiwk.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.75,0:22:20.75,MK英文,,0,0,0,,He doesn't mean his talent is a cook.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.97,0:22:22.25,MK英文,,0,0,0,,But as a mechanic.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.50,0:22:23.92,MK英文,,0,0,0,,Am I right, Jonas?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.95,0:22:31.82,MK英文,,0,0,0,,{\i1}You stand right in baby{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.55,0:22:35.10,MK英文,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But I'll come back to you{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.45,0:22:40.40,MK英文,,0,0,0,,{\i1}She gave me a basic five will be alright
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.57,0:22:43.25,MK英文,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Baby, whoop!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.82,0:22:59.72,OP中文,,0,0,0,,我们在零重力之中起舞
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.95,0:23:03.42,OP中文,,0,0,0,,飞速旅行到遥远的星际
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.60,0:23:05.97,OP中文,,0,0,0,,Malo Korrigan
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.77,0:23:09.80,OP中文,,0,0,0,,没人能打倒你
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.00,0:23:12.48,OP中文,,0,0,0,,Malo Korrigan
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.32,0:23:15.37,OP中文,,0,0,0,,生活在宇宙中
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.82,0:22:59.72,OP英文,,0,0,0,,We can dance in zero G{\pos(480,45)}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.95,0:23:03.42,OP英文,,0,0,0,,Traveling fast far from galaxy{\pos(480,45)}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.60,0:23:05.97,OP英文,,0,0,0,,Malo Korrigan{\pos(480,45)}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.77,0:23:09.80,OP英文,,0,0,0,,Nobody will bring you down{\pos(480,45)}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.00,0:23:12.48,OP英文,,0,0,0,,Malo Korrigan{\pos(480,45)}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.32,0:23:15.37,OP英文,,0,0,0,,live in space{\pos(480,45)}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.80,0:01:23.17,MK字幕,,0,0,0,,Jonas 别让那些推进器坏掉
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.22,0:01:33.97,MK字幕,,0,0,0,,就像是风暴里的一片沙
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.75,0:01:36.35,MK字幕,,0,0,0,,我正在想着怎么把它放进去
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.57,0:01:39.72,MK字幕,,0,0,0,,感觉就像冰激凌筒的圆锥
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.75,0:01:42.02,MK字幕,,0,0,0,,卡在火山口似的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.60,0:01:45.02,MK字幕,,0,0,0,,这个黑色的钛合金燃料电池
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.02,0:01:47.00,MK字幕,,0,0,0,,像是快用了一万亿光年了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.02,0:01:48.95,MK字幕,,0,0,0,,难道没有保修吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.32,0:01:51.82,MK字幕,,0,0,0,,孩子 你开玩笑吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.77,0:01:54.75,MK字幕,,0,0,0,,我从你那些不信神的兄弟那儿买来的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.77,0:01:56.50,MK字幕,,0,0,0,,甚至没付钱
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.75,0:01:59.50,MK字幕,,0,0,0,,老伙计抓稳了 因为我们要硬着陆了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.97,0:02:27.97,MK字幕,,0,0,0,,Jonas 让1 2 3号反推引擎满推力点火
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.25,0:03:10.82,MK字幕,,0,0,0,,你很棒啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.67,0:03:16.05,MK字幕,,0,0,0,,尽管状况很糟糕但你还是撑过来了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.32,0:03:40.52,MK字幕,,0,0,0,,公主你不该穿着太空服吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.67,0:03:43.30,MK字幕,,0,0,0,,这个星球的大气不是很好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.60,0:03:44.50,MK字幕,,0,0,0,,对你而言不是很好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.67,0:03:48.40,MK字幕,,0,0,0,,不过我还是挺喜欢呼吸这温度在零下的一氧化碳气体
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.70,0:03:49.80,MK字幕,,0,0,0,,所以有什么问题
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.65,0:03:52.30,MK字幕,,0,0,0,,我来告诉你是什么问题
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.37,0:03:56.17,MK字幕,,0,0,0,,在这片行星级的垃圾场上找一个钛合金燃料电池
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.35,0:03:57.77,MK字幕,,0,0,0,,这可不是垃圾场
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.77,0:03:59.25,MK字幕,,0,0,0,,这更像是一个博物馆
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.50,0:04:03.30,MK字幕,,0,0,0,,各种各样在Sewalik Wars中使用过的载具和武器
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.30,0:04:05.65,MK字幕,,0,0,0,,现在都聚集在这座星球上腐烂着
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.95,0:04:19.52,MK字幕,,0,0,0,,天哪
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.52,0:04:21.85,MK字幕,,0,0,0,,热防护盾在我们着陆时被烧坏了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.47,0:04:24.60,MK字幕,,0,0,0,,所以我现在需要进行些额外的维修
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.35,0:04:34.20,MK字幕,,0,0,0,,{\i1}我想成为你的恋人{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.20,0:04:38.97,MK字幕,,0,0,0,,{\i1}也许你不想这样但我还是迷恋着你{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.50,0:04:42.32,MK字幕,,0,0,0,,{\i1}可你还在哭着{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.57,0:04:43.65,MK字幕,,0,0,0,,需要我们等你吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.72,0:04:44.47,MK字幕,,0,0,0,,不用了 谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.67,0:04:46.62,MK字幕,,0,0,0,,去找那个钛合金燃料电池吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.77,0:04:48.07,MK字幕,,0,0,0,,要Mk.87型号的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.10,0:04:50.87,MK字幕,,0,0,0,,我修完的时候会四处找找的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.00,0:04:53.27,MK字幕,,0,0,0,,我有九成把握比你先找到
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.67,0:04:54.35,MK字幕,,0,0,0,,哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.57,0:04:57.57,MK字幕,,0,0,0,,Cyana 你打赌吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.52,0:05:00.47,MK字幕,,0,0,0,,你俩
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.50,0:05:03.45,MK字幕,,0,0,0,,应该带上最好的东西 以防万一
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.57,0:05:05.60,MK字幕,,0,0,0,,不用了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.60,0:05:07.27,MK字幕,,0,0,0,,你的质子枪
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.30,0:05:09.07,MK字幕,,0,0,0,,甚至比过热的核反应堆还危险
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.50,0:05:15.52,MK字幕,,0,0,0,,再见
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.20,0:06:00.77,MK字幕,,0,0,0,,看看这些太空战船
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.82,0:06:02.82,MK字幕,,0,0,0,,中子导弹和无人轰炸机
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.95,0:06:04.20,MK字幕,,0,0,0,,这个地方很疯狂
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.32,0:06:05.87,MK字幕,,0,0,0,,战争总是很疯狂
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.92,0:06:08.25,MK字幕,,0,0,0,,而Sewalik Wars是最疯狂的战争
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.45,0:06:12.17,MK字幕,,0,0,0,,另外一方面 12个母星厌倦了战争
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.47,0:06:15.40,MK字幕,,0,0,0,,于是他们决定联合起来
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.62,0:06:18.75,MK字幕,,0,0,0,,这就是星际联盟诞生的原因
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.00,0:06:20.00,MK字幕,,0,0,0,,让我试试
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.77,0:06:27.32,MK字幕,,0,0,0,,我喜欢被当众羞辱
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.42,0:06:29.02,MK字幕,,0,0,0,,看起来我赢得了赌局
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.35,0:06:32.25,MK字幕,,0,0,0,,嘿 Jonas Mk.75型号兼容吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.44,0:06:33.62,MK字幕,,0,0,0,,你觉得我会因为赌局
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.67,0:06:35.07,MK字幕,,0,0,0,,而说这个型号不行
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.07,0:06:36.70,MK字幕,,0,0,0,,但实际上我们至少需要两个Mk.87型号
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.97,0:06:37.62,MK字幕,,0,0,0,,你确定吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.87,0:06:39.57,MK字幕,,0,0,0,,以前在学校学习的时候我了解到这都是兼容的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.57,0:06:41.20,MK字幕,,0,0,0,,忘记你以前在学校学过的那些东西
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.27,0:06:44.05,MK字幕,,0,0,0,,那些迂腐的教授从来没进过引擎舱
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.45,0:06:45.45,MK字幕,,0,0,0,,而且 我有...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.50,0:06:50.25,MK字幕,,0,0,0,,Jonas
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.42,0:06:53.25,MK字幕,,0,0,0,,Jonas 回答我
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.65,0:06:54.22,MK字幕,,0,0,0,,Jonas
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.60,0:06:55.52,MK字幕,,0,0,0,,他没回音
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.62,0:06:56.32,MK字幕,,0,0,0,,咋回事
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.62,0:06:58.25,MK字幕,,0,0,0,,我们走
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.47,0:07:11.92,MK字幕,,0,0,0,,Cyana 小心点
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.25,0:07:14.07,MK字幕,,0,0,0,,你不知道往下走会走到哪儿
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.95,0:07:23.05,MK字幕,,0,0,0,,Jonas
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.05,0:07:39.25,MK字幕,,0,0,0,,Jonas你在哪儿
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.32,0:07:50.52,MK字幕,,0,0,0,,Jonas
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.05,0:07:57.40,MK字幕,,0,0,0,,你发现了什么
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.72,0:08:00.65,MK字幕,,0,0,0,,我们整货舱的全息屏幕都不见了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.10,0:08:02.65,MK字幕,,0,0,0,,Jonas也不见了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.05,0:08:12.02,MK字幕,,0,0,0,,Malo 也许有个方法能定位到Jonas
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.05,0:08:13.60,MK字幕,,0,0,0,,我听着呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.00,0:08:15.90,MK字幕,,0,0,0,,如果他的通讯器还在工作
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.97,0:08:18.17,MK字幕,,0,0,0,,在他的频率上 我们能对准并靠近他
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.47,0:08:23.35,MK字幕,,0,0,0,,好的 这起作用了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.72,0:08:25.22,MK字幕,,0,0,0,,他的信号在我们的前方
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.52,0:08:27.20,MK字幕,,0,0,0,,距离5千米
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.82,0:08:28.52,MK字幕,,0,0,0,,现在在移动
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.40,0:08:34.77,MK字幕,,0,0,0,,坚持住啊 老牛仔
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.60,0:08:36.62,MK字幕,,0,0,0,,我们在路上了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.67,0:08:54.77,MK字幕,,0,0,0,,距离2千米 我们正在接近
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.67,0:09:15.67,MK字幕,,0,0,0,,现在信号离我们非常近了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.12,0:09:17.75,MK字幕,,0,0,0,,但为什么我们还没找到他
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.42,0:09:19.75,MK字幕,,0,0,0,,Jonas
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.10,0:09:22.72,MK字幕,,0,0,0,,这是个不好笑的玩笑
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.05,0:09:23.82,MK字幕,,0,0,0,,哦不
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.32,0:09:31.95,MK字幕,,0,0,0,,信号并不是从这发出来的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.17,0:09:32.97,MK字幕,,0,0,0,,他也许还好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.05,0:09:33.97,MK字幕,,0,0,0,,在没有头盔的情况下吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.32,0:09:37.22,MK字幕,,0,0,0,,我能在寒冷的一氧化碳大气中生存
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.27,0:09:38.35,MK字幕,,0,0,0,,但Jonas不行
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.32,0:09:50.02,MK字幕,,0,0,0,,Jonas
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.15,0:10:11.87,MK字幕,,0,0,0,,Cyana 信号再次移动了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.17,0:10:13.82,MK字幕,,0,0,0,,老伙计还活着
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.97,0:10:15.47,MK字幕,,0,0,0,,他可能就在那边
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.45,0:10:42.37,MK字幕,,0,0,0,,快离开那儿
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.65,0:11:02.25,MK字幕,,0,0,0,,小心
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.55,0:11:13.45,MK字幕,,0,0,0,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.07,0:12:03.12,MK字幕,,0,0,0,,Cyana
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.35,0:12:07.57,MK字幕,,0,0,0,,我们在哪儿
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.35,0:12:11.67,MK字幕,,0,0,0,,在XP级别的运输船里
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.87,0:12:14.57,MK字幕,,0,0,0,,在Sewalik Wars中使用的最大的飞船之一
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.30,0:12:19.37,MK字幕,,0,0,0,,我还能收到信号
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.80,0:12:21.27,MK字幕,,0,0,0,,Jonas还在附近
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.70,0:12:22.70,MK字幕,,0,0,0,,我们去找找看
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.45,0:12:26.20,MK字幕,,0,0,0,,你知道那个攻击我们的东西是什么吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.87,0:12:29.45,MK字幕,,0,0,0,,也许是大战中遗留下来的战斗机器人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.80,0:12:31.75,MK字幕,,0,0,0,,但我以为所有武器都被关闭了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.75,0:12:32.90,MK字幕,,0,0,0,,在遗弃在这里之前
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.22,0:12:35.80,MK字幕,,0,0,0,,看起来有些人打算违反规定
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.67,0:12:39.90,MK字幕,,0,0,0,,如果这是真的 那我们应该告知有关方面
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.02,0:12:41.25,MK字幕,,0,0,0,,Malo 瞧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.57,0:12:44.65,MK字幕,,0,0,0,,这就是我们丢失的货物 全息屏幕
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.40,0:12:51.22,MK字幕,,0,0,0,,但为什么它们被放在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.55,0:12:52.32,MK字幕,,0,0,0,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.82,0:12:59.65,MK字幕,,0,0,0,,不要动
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.00,0:13:13.62,MK字幕,,0,0,0,,走
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.57,0:13:25.50,MK字幕,,0,0,0,,战斗单位FAR422的任务是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.50,0:13:29.57,MK字幕,,0,0,0,,防御前线战场并击退任何对友军的攻击
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.57,0:13:34.70,MK字幕,,0,0,0,,BA2568A125遭受到了敌人的攻击
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.75,0:13:36.35,MK字幕,,0,0,0,,入侵者已被消灭
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.35,0:13:38.35,MK字幕,,0,0,0,,尝试联系指挥部
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.40,0:13:41.17,MK字幕,,0,0,0,,并请求立即援助
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.60,0:13:42.22,MK字幕,,0,0,0,,真厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.45,0:13:44.72,MK字幕,,0,0,0,,他仍认为自己在Sewalik Wars中战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.97,0:13:47.87,MK字幕,,0,0,0,,我认为有些愚蠢的将军没有把他正确地关闭
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.45,0:14:01.77,MK字幕,,0,0,0,,Jonas还在附近
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.42,0:14:26.07,MK字幕,,0,0,0,,跟我来
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.62,0:14:40.52,MK字幕,,0,0,0,,这都是些什么
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.72,0:14:41.65,MK字幕,,0,0,0,,嘘 安静
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.20,0:14:47.87,MK字幕,,0,0,0,,更多的战斗机器人 将近一个中队的数量
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.57,0:14:58.17,MK字幕,,0,0,0,,战斗单位FAR422无法联系到指挥部
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.07,0:15:06.27,MK字幕,,0,0,0,,战斗单位FAR422的任务是防御前线战场
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.97,0:15:09.12,MK字幕,,0,0,0,,执行技术性操作
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.12,0:15:11.72,MK字幕,,0,0,0,,以获得必要的援兵
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.72,0:15:36.16,MK字幕,,0,0,0,,这个金属的怪兽正在通过我们的货物
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.16,0:15:38.22,MK字幕,,0,0,0,,重启其他机器人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.62,0:15:39.87,MK字幕,,0,0,0,,这些就是援兵
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.22,0:15:42.12,MK字幕,,0,0,0,,他在为自己建造一个军队
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.00,0:15:47.30,MK字幕,,0,0,0,,嘿
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.60,0:15:48.10,MK字幕,,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.22,0:15:50.35,MK字幕,,0,0,0,,他的操作方式和Jonas一样
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.72,0:15:55.57,MK字幕,,0,0,0,,Jonas的信号就在我们下面
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.62,0:15:57.65,MK字幕,,0,0,0,,但那就是机器人的位置
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.75,0:15:59.45,MK字幕,,0,0,0,,Jonas在机器人里
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.95,0:16:01.05,MK字幕,,0,0,0,,我们该怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.55,0:16:02.47,MK字幕,,0,0,0,,我们把他救出来
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.27,0:16:03.60,MK字幕,,0,0,0,,快来
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.95,0:16:27.45,MK字幕,,0,0,0,,战斗单位FAR422被敌军攻击
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.70,0:16:32.25,MK字幕,,0,0,0,,任务是保护友军并立刻消灭入侵者
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.72,0:17:03.22,MK字幕,,0,0,0,,你确定这是个好主意吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.25,0:17:04.95,MK字幕,,0,0,0,,不是 但这是我唯一能想到的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.00,0:17:08.95,MK字幕,,0,0,0,,消灭入侵者 消灭入侵者
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.57,0:17:49.02,MK字幕,,0,0,0,,消灭入侵者 消灭入侵者 消灭入侵者
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.02,0:17:53.52,MK字幕,,0,0,0,,跟着我
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.40,0:18:22.97,MK字幕,,0,0,0,,Jonas 你能听见我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.87,0:18:32.15,MK字幕,,0,0,0,,战斗单位FAR422...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.92,0:18:40.55,MK字幕,,0,0,0,,Jonas
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.90,0:18:51.17,MK字幕,,0,0,0,,情况很糟糕
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.72,0:18:53.70,MK字幕,,0,0,0,,机器人正在把Jonas脑中的数据
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.70,0:18:55.97,MK字幕,,0,0,0,,下载到他自己的系统里
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.85,0:19:01.02,MK字幕,,0,0,0,,老伙计 坚持住
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.15,0:19:03.20,MK字幕,,0,0,0,,%$^%@#
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.12,0:19:13.25,MK字幕,,0,0,0,,诶 诶
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.22,0:19:15.70,MK字幕,,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.45,0:19:18.97,MK字幕,,0,0,0,,中央处理器是由财团制造的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.32,0:19:22.50,MK字幕,,0,0,0,,但是Sewalik Wars期间财团还不存在
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.75,0:19:25.10,MK字幕,,0,0,0,,我怀疑我们的朋友Yago控制了这个机器人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.10,0:19:27.20,MK字幕,,0,0,0,,来为财团制造一个秘密军队
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.85,0:19:28.95,MK字幕,,0,0,0,,但是他失败了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.05,0:19:38.52,MK字幕,,0,0,0,,消灭入侵者 消灭入侵者 消灭入侵者
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.87,0:20:35.35,MK字幕,,0,0,0,,Jonas
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.12,0:20:38.70,MK字幕,,0,0,0,,Jonas
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.15,0:20:42.12,MK字幕,,0,0,0,,能说话吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.05,0:20:51.87,MK字幕,,0,0,0,,看起来我最后还是赢得了赌局
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.60,0:20:53.00,MK字幕,,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.17,0:20:55.27,MK字幕,,0,0,0,,看看那儿
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.07,0:20:57.67,MK字幕,,0,0,0,,钛合金燃料电池
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.75,0:20:58.80,MK字幕,,0,0,0,,是Mk.87型号的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.95,0:20:59.95,MK字幕,,0,0,0,,没错我找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.60,0:21:03.82,MK字幕,,0,0,0,,Jonas你真是狡猾
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.82,0:21:06.30,MK字幕,,0,0,0,,这还有很多Mk.87型号的电池
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.00,0:21:09.85,MK字幕,,0,0,0,,也许以后能卖给你那不信神的老兄
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.55,0:21:13.30,MK字幕,,0,0,0,,这回我们收获颇丰
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.45,0:21:19.72,MK字幕,,0,0,0,,但首先我想修理一下我们的机器人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.77,0:21:20.52,MK字幕,,0,0,0,,你开玩笑吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.97,0:21:24.47,MK字幕,,0,0,0,,FAR422这回算是彻底销毁了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.85,0:21:26.07,MK字幕,,0,0,0,,你是这么认为的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.17,0:21:29.07,MK字幕,,0,0,0,,但我比你以为的还要狡猾
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.00,0:21:33.57,MK字幕,,0,0,0,,因为这个机器人的品位不错 尝试着下载我的知识
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.85,0:21:36.00,MK字幕,,0,0,0,,我认为应该教他点技巧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.07,0:21:39.62,MK字幕,,0,0,0,,并抹掉所有关于Sewalik Wars或者财团的记忆
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.32,0:21:52.92,MK字幕,,0,0,0,,{\u1}quiberon quasars {\u0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.92,0:21:54.20,MK字幕,,0,0,0,,我有失败过吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.20,0:21:54.72,MK字幕,,0,0,0,,很好
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.20,0:22:00.67,MK字幕,,0,0,0,,当我困在那个巨大的金属机器人里的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.37,0:22:04.62,MK字幕,,0,0,0,,我以为我再也不能逃出来了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.47,0:22:09.47,MK字幕,,0,0,0,,Jonas 顺便问一下 你教了那个机器人什么技巧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.55,0:22:13.50,MK字幕,,0,0,0,,没啥特别复杂的 就是一些基本的和平的程序
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.60,0:22:16.62,MK字幕,,0,0,0,,但是我确实把我最好的才能给了他
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.07,0:22:18.30,MK字幕,,0,0,0,,Kiwk Kiwk 别笑
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.75,0:22:20.75,MK字幕,,0,0,0,,这不意味着他最好的才能是做饭
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.97,0:22:22.25,MK字幕,,0,0,0,,但应该是维修方面的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.50,0:22:23.92,MK字幕,,0,0,0,,我说得对吗 Jonas
